fields.title: Digital World
fields.description: The first course to the digital world

Say Hello


Write a function that takes in a name as a param and return "Hello, <name>!". 

Sample:

>>> hello("Tom")

# return "Hello, Tom"

First program

Write a program that accepts a string S and prints "Hello, S"
Which of the following types is immutable?
demonstrate how to identify an individual input's uniqueness.
